      "required": false,
      "helpText": "Enter the narrative that should be sent to PCE when this selection is scanned.  This will be the provider narrative that is shown in PCE and Problem List.  If there is no entry in this field the text as it appears on the form will be sent as the narrative.  This field can only be entered for the type of interfaces that allow adding this narrative, and then send the narrative to PCE. ",
